<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>يا ابن هشامٍ أهلكَ الناس اللبَنْ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>انظر قافية<span class="c1">" وَقَرَنْ"</span>.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
